# Dill Yogurt Dip


## Ingredients

## 1 cup Greek yogurt
## 2 tablespoons fresh dill
## 1/4 preserved lemon, seeds removed
## Salt and Pepper to taste

## Method

## 1. Finely chop the fresh dill and the lemon and add them into a bowl. 
## 2. Add the remaining ingredients plus a bit of water to thin out the yogurt. 
## 3. Taste and adjust to your liking. 
